calculation_formula: CASE WHEN EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM sunscreen_application WHERE sunscreen_application.date = target_date AND sunscreen_application.time <= sunlight_exposure.time AND (sunlight_exposure.time - sunscreen_application.time) <= 30) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END FROM sunlight_exposure WHERE DATE(datetime_combined) = target_date
description: Individual sunscreen compliance for each sun exposure session
name: Sunscreen Compliance Events

calculation_formula: CASE WHEN COUNT(daily_sunlight_exposure_sessions) = 0 THEN 100 ELSE (SUM(sunscreen_compliance_events) / COUNT(sunlight_exposure)) * 100 END WHERE DATE(datetime_combined) = target_date
description: Percentage of sun exposure sessions with proper sunscreen application
name: Daily Sunscreen Compliance Rate
